Schedule data is derived from publicly published timetables and rules
released by:
- STASY (https://www.stasy.gr) — metro and tram
- OASA (https://www.oasa.gr) — Saturday 24-hour service, fare prices
- Hellenic Train (https://www.hellenictrain.gr) — suburban railway

These sources are the authoritative answer. Syrmos is not affiliated
with STASY, OASA, Hellenic Train, or any Greek transport authority.
Re-publishing schedule data here is done in good faith as a derived
factual compilation; trademarks of the named operators remain their
own property.

Live train positions are obtained from Hellenic Train's public SSE
feed at railway.gov.gr. The feed is consumed in good faith for
non-commercial display under Hellenic Train's published terms.

